# Editors
# =============================================================================
## VS Code — keep shared settings, ignore personal/generated
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/*.code-snippets
.vscode/settings.json.user

